2.2.1 3scale hereby provides Customer with a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable and terminable license to access and use 3scale’s API Management solution (“Software”) solely for Customer’s operations.

Customer’s operations include the right to allow Customer’s customer access to the Software interfaces to transact business with Customer.

Customer may permit its third party contractors, ~[subject to confidentiality and use obligations at least as restrictive as those set forth in this Agreement,~] to access and use the Software ~[solely in connection with services provided by such third party contractors to Customer]~.
